{"tid":2225704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日好似冇咩事發生，曱甴好克制","createTime":"2020-10-01T13:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T14:03:43.000Z","uid":196227,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5517af803a6183cdf25c588f3993f1ae4c1ea207","tid":2225704,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nEIFEU5nrVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnEIFEU5nrVc&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=0d2e845e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nEIFEU5nrVc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身粗口、呼喝、阻街、大圍捕鳩拉<br />\n我都唔撚提，係直播可以見到好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢單野係大紀元見到<br />\n前因冇片未清楚<br />\n但係片中男人好合作，主動話拉我<br />\n冇任何反抗，主動提出埋比你拉<br />\n班曱甴痴撚咗線一定要整低你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知外國又會點睇，有冇人推到比外國議員<br />\n利申Twitter 睇唔到，我英文又差<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日班狗絕對比之前仆街<br />\n現場氣氛已經好溫和都變到咁"},{"pid":"687719296cc28e01e7a3c90fc0d9f2b6dde645e1","tid":2225704,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀標題黨"},{"pid":"8b9a55e43c5ee30f2b71e175de20bb505ba7415b","tid":2225704,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59003be44e145b03335f0410a4e1551eac450d54","tid":2225704,"uid":196227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:31:37.000Z","msg":"今日個twitter好似靜撚咗咁<br />\n<br />\n班狗明明依然咁仆街"},{"pid":"e7374bfb62c91f5fcac155b385266967d6f4c58e","tid":2225704,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"687719296cc28e01e7a3c90fc0d9f2b6dde645e1","tid":2225704,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"